  "kind": "Theorem",
  "title": "Truth-Table Validity Test for Argument Forms",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "An argument form \\((\\Gamma,\\varphi)\\) is valid if and only if no row of its truth\ntable makes every formula in \\(\\Gamma\\) true and \\(\\varphi\\) false.",
